d see around in Vienna, or before the War in Prague. And she was rather sad, and, of course, not being blind [at that time]. And also, she\rquote d sort of come down so far \'85 she was like a kind of \'85
 these political refugees that come, she was a bit like that. She\rquote d got no position, she just arrived, and we looked after her for a few months.
