d go off, and we\rquote d fly up over Snowdon and \'85 pretty all for nothing! So I really enjoyed that. I mean, it was sort of terrific fun. And so when it came to go into National Service, I delayed a bit to do athletics, which is a sort of \'85
 I just had a good time, really. So it wasn\rquote t until I was 19 that I actually went into the National Service.
