d be the focus groups and all of this, you know, that\rquote s the way it\rquote s done now. But it was a kind of a \'85 just getting \'85 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 just getting the feel of it}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 . \'93What sort of place is this?\'94 I could be criticised for being incredibly subjective, because it was really a bit arbitrary about to whom one spoke. I obviously tried to get a \'85 so one would say, \'93
Well, I haven\rquote t talked to anybody up on the council estate\'94, and you\rquote d sort
