\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid15929336\charrsid2767477 Ray:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 Well, overall, I started the Nuffield thing about \rquote 
78, and we carried on, on and off, for ten years. But I really got to know the place. But the main time, of course, was between \rquote 80 and \rquote 83. Those three years were very, very heavy indeed. And at the same time, Claire and I were sort of \'85
 I mean, I was anxious to get her publication and stuff, to justify \'85 so we went off to [the ISA Congress] Mexico City to give a paper, and at that time, I was still slightly in the urban area, and so we \'85
