\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477  came out in 1984, which is very close to the end of the project. And so Sir Douglas Hague, who was Chairman of the ESRC, and was friendly with Mrs. Thatcher, was looking for some evidence to
