t, because the thing is sewn up. The local window cleaner will just knock the ladder from under you, if you go out there and try and compete\'94, and you know, he\rquote 
d get a broken leg. Because it is very tough. So, about a year later, I went back to the same house, and she opened the door, and I thought I\rquote d come to the wrong house, because the staircase had moved, and it was all different. And it turned out he
