\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477  was a big effort to do at the time, and so I think one just gasps for breath a bit after that, and didn\rquote t go back into the ethnography, to write \'85 if I had nothing else to do, if I wasn\rquote 
t on the UGC at the same time, and if I\rquote d been a sort of more junior researcher, I\rquote d have lived off that for years, writing little articles, as people do, on different aspects. And, you kn
ow, one could still, you know, you follow the debate in the literature, you see a gap in it, and put your own stuff in, and away you go. But I\rquote m not that sort of sociologist.
