\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid5903709\charrsid2767477 Ray:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 Absolutely! Misplaced respect puts it well \'85 as if there\rquote s some kind of truth, and that socio
logy has got it, and, you know, the great sociologists \'85 So people come, and embarrass me they come in and knock on my door in the university, and say, you know, \'93We\rquote ve read your books in\'94 whatever it is, \'93and we\rquote 
ve got to come and talk to you about them\'94, and sort of \'93Say something wise, Oh King!\'94
