\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 Michele}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 :\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 
So, moving on, because we started talking about {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Eastern Europe{\*\xmlclose}, and that had come from setting up the university in 1992, was it? In {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Eastern Europe{\*\xmlclose}?

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid5903709\charrsid2767477 Ray:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 Yes.
