d done the work a long time before that, in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 the Managers and their Wives}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 , why did those ideas come out again?
