\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 Michele}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 :\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 I wan
ted to move on to another subject now, really, and ask you about art collecting, because you clearly are a great art collector. So, fire away!
