\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid5903709\charrsid2767477 Ray:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 No, I don\rquote t think \'85 I honestly don\rquote t talk about it quite a lot. In fact, a lot of my
 colleagues wouldn\rquote t have known that I collected art. In fact, some people that knew that I\rquote d got so much stuff, so, of course, \'93Ray\rquote s interested in prints\'94, which, of course, I\rquote m not. But it means they\rquote 
