And I may have mentioned this before, that, in a sense, one ought to get oneself totally analysed, and present the case as oneself, so here\rquote s my research instrument, it\rquote s myself analysed. Now, with this research instrument, I\rquote 
m now going to give an account. Now, that is quite different from the kind of quantitative research which other sociologists would do with it \'85 all sort of personal area I was completely irrelevant. They would simply say, \'93How good is the data set?
