\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 Michele}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 :\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1197548\charrsid2767477 But would you have been satisfied?
