 okay, let\rquote s get really arrogant! If you\rquote re \'85 you struggle away at the so and so grammar school, and you go to the \'85 was Polytechnic, but now University of Whatever, and you scrap
e a 2:1, and you go off and you teach in secondary schools for a bit, and then you come back and you do a part-time MA, (forgive the arrogance), and then the Polytechnic University takes you back as a Junior Lecturer, and you toil away in that narrow area
